discuss /dɪˈskʌs/

(discussing,discussed,discusses) 

1. V-T If people discuss something, they talk about it, often in order to reach a decision. 讨论 

例： I will be discussing the situation with colleagues tomorrow. 我将于明天和同事们讨论这个情况。 

2. V-T If you discuss something, you write or talk about it in detail. 详述 

例： I will discuss the role of diet in cancer prevention in Chapter 

7. 我将在第7章详述饮食在癌症预防中的作用。

